#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to play"
msgstr "Kuidas mängida"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Objective:"
msgstr "Eesmärk:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Eliminate all Opponents."
msgstr "Kõrvaldada kõik vastased."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Each player is provided with five keys that they use to move their "
#| "character and lay bombs. For example, the default keys for Player 1 are "
#| "the Up, Down, Left and Right arrow keys to move respectively in those "
#| "directions, and the &Enter; key to lay a bomb. Please refer to the <link "
#| "linkend=\"config_player\">Player Configuration</link> Section to find "
#| "shortcut keys for other players, as well as how to configure them."
msgid ""
"Each player is provided with five keys that they use to move their character "
"and lay bombs. For example, the default keys for Player 1 are the &Up;, "
"&Down;, &Left; and &Right; arrow keys to move respectively in those "
"directions, and the &Enter; key to lay a bomb. Please refer to the <link "
"linkend=\"config_player\">Player Configuration</link> Section to find "
"shortcut keys for other players, as well as how to configure them."
msgstr ""
"Igale mängijale on eraldatud viis klahvi, millega nad saavad liigutada oma "
"tegelast ning asetada pomme. Vaikimisi on mängija 1 klahvideks neli "
"nooleklahvi, mis liigutavad tegelast vastavas suunas, ning klahv &Enter; "
"pommide asetamiseks. Teiste mängijate klahve näeb ning saab seadistada "
"seadistustedialoogi sektsioonis <link linkend=\"config_player\">Mängija</"
"link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The purpose of laying bombs, aside from attacking other opponents, is to "
"destroy the many blocks scattered throughout the arena in order to clear a "
"path or uncover hidden bonuses. Among the many bonuses that can be uncovered "
"are those that make you move faster or increase your bomb blast range; the "
"more bonuses of this type you collect, the easier it is to eliminate your "
"opponents and win the round. But be warned that just as many handicaps exist "
"that can turn the tide against you, including those that slow you down or "
"invert your moving keys."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks vastaste ründamisele on pommide asetamine vajalik ka areenile "
"puistatud plokkide likvideerimiseks, et puhastada endale teed või leida üles "
"peidetud boonused. Arvukate boonuste seas on sellised, mis lubavad liikuda "
"kiiremini või suurendavad sinu pommide plahvatusjõudu. Mida rohkem boonuseid "
"kogud, seda hõlpsam on kõrvaldada vastaseid ja võita voor. Kuid arvesta, et "
"sama hästi võid leida ka takistusi, mis aeglustavad sinu liikumist või "
"vahetavad ära liikumisklahvid."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:74
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each won round, the player is awarded a point. The first player to win a "
"predefined number of points (the default is 3), wins the game!"
msgstr ""
"Iga võidetud vooru eest saab mängija punkti. Mängu võidab mängija, kes kogub "
"esimesena eelnevalt kindlaks määratud arvu punkte (vaikimisi 3)."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid "Game Rules, Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Mängureeglid, strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Items"
msgstr "Elemendid"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:83
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Arena"
msgstr "Areen"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid "The players are in an arena which consists of:"
msgstr "Mängijad asuvad areenil, mis koosneb järgmistest osadest:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:90
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Wall"
msgstr "Areeni sein"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Wall &ndash; this defines the outline of the arena map and cannot be "
"destroyed."
msgstr "Sein määratleb areeni välised piirid ning seda ei saa hävitada."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Ground"
msgstr "Areeni pind"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:98
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Ground &ndash; this can be walked on safely."
msgstr "Pind on piirkond, kus saab turvaliselt liikuda."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Ice"
msgstr "Areeni jää"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Ice &ndash; this will make the ground slippery. The speed increases on "
"the ice and it is not possible to completly stop moving."
msgstr ""
"Jää muudab pinna libedaks. Kiirus suureneb jääl ning liikumist ei saagi "
"täielikult peatada."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Block"
msgstr "Areeni plokk"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Block &ndash; this can be destroyed with a bomb, and may contain a bonus "
"(or a handicap)."
msgstr ""
"Plokke saab hävitada pommiga ning need võivad sisaldada boonuseid (või ka "
"takistusi)."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Bomb Mortar"
msgstr "Areeni pommipilduja"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Bomb Mortar &ndash; this will throw bombs that are placed on it to "
"random places."
msgstr "Pommipilduja heidab pomme juhuslikesse kohtadesse."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:125
#, no-c-format
msgid "Arena Arrow Right"
msgstr "Areeni nool paremale"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Arrows &ndash; this will move the bombs that are placed on it to the "
"direction they point."
msgstr "Nooled liigutavad pomme suunas, kuhu nad osutavad."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:129
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If there is none of the above items, there is a hole at the ground and "
"moving into it will result in falling into the deep and die. The same "
"applies also if there is no wall at the edge of the arena and the player "
"moves outside of the arena."
msgstr ""
"Kui tegemist ei ole ühegi mainitud elemendiga, siis on sinu ees pinnas olev "
"auk, mille peale liikudes kukud sisse ja sured. Sama juhtub siis, kui "
"areenil pole seina ja sa liigud areenilt välja."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:134
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Bonuses"
msgstr "Boonused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bonuses are helpful for reaching the game goal and effects exists permanent "
"- even after a handicap disappears. Currently there are following bonuses:"
msgstr ""
"Boonused on abiks mängu eesmärgi saavutamisel ning nende efektid jäävad "
"püsima ka pärast seda, kui nende mõju on ajutiselt mõne takistuse tõttu "
"kahanenud. Praegu on olemas järgmised boonused:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Speed"
msgstr "Kiiruseboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed &ndash; increases your speed slightly."
msgstr "Kiirus suurendab veidi sinu liikumiskiirust."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Bomb"
msgstr "Pommiboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Bomb &ndash; adds an extra bomb to your arsenal, allowing you to lay more "
"than one bomb at a time."
msgstr ""
"Pomm annab sinu arsenali lisapommi, mis võimaldab korraga asetada rohkem kui "
"ühe pommi."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Power"
msgstr "Võimsusboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Power &ndash; increases the power of your bombs, extending their bomb blast "
"range."
msgstr "Võimsus suurendab pommi võimsust, laiendades plahvatuse mõjuala."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:162
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Shield"
msgstr "Kilbiboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shield &ndash; makes invincible for one bomb blast."
msgstr "Kilp kaitseb sind ühe pommiplahvatuse eest."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Throw"
msgstr "Heiteboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:170
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Throw &ndash; adds the ability to throw bombs. Just press the key for laying "
"bombs while a bomb is below you."
msgstr ""
"Heitmine annab võimaluse pomme heita. Vajuta lihtsalt pommi asetamise "
"klahvi, kui pomm asub sinu all."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Kick"
msgstr "Tõukamisboonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kick &ndash; adds the ability to move bombs. Just run against an bomb and "
"the bomb will move."
msgstr ""
"Tõukamine annab võimaluse pomme liigutada. Jookse lihtsalt pommi pihta ja "
"see liigub paigast."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Handicaps"
msgstr "Takistused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Handicaps are the opposite of bonuses and hinder the player. The good thing "
"is that effects get lost after some time (other than bonuses) and the player "
"can play in is usual behavior (including bonuses) again. Currently there are "
"following handicaps:"
msgstr ""
"Erinevalt boonustest takistused muudavad mängija elu raskemaks. Õnneks "
"erinevalt boonustest nende mõju kaob mõne aja pärast ning mängija saab taas "
"tavapäraselt edasi mängida (ning kasutada ka kõiki boonuseid, mis tal on). "
"Praegu on olemas järgmised takistused:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Slow"
msgstr "Aeglustakistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid "Slow &ndash; makes you move very slowly."
msgstr "Aeglus muudab kogu liikumise väga aeglaseks."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Hyperactive"
msgstr "Hüperaktiivsuse takistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:197
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hyperactive &ndash; makes you move a little TOO fast."
msgstr "Hüperaktiivsus paneb LIIGA kiiresti liikuma."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Mirror"
msgstr "Peegeldamistakistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Mirror &ndash; inverts your moving keys, so that up becomes down and left "
"becomes right."
msgstr ""
"Peegeldamine muudab liikumisklahvid vastupidiseks, nii et noolt üles "
"vajutades liigud alla, noolt vasakule vajutades aga paremale."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Scatty"
msgstr "Hajameelsustakistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scatty &ndash; forces you to continuously lay bombs without control."
msgstr "Hajameelsus sunnib pidevalt ka vastu tahtmist pomme asetama."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:217
#, no-c-format
msgid "Handicap Restrain"
msgstr "Vaoshoituse takistus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restrain &ndash; prevents you to lay bombs."
msgstr "Vaoshoitus takistab pomme asetamast."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "The ambivalent Items"
msgstr "Ambivalentsed elemendid"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This type of bonuses are neither good nor bad, it mostly depends on the "
"environment. Currently there are following neutral bonuses:"
msgstr ""
"Need boonused ei ole õieti head ega halvad, sõltudes rohkem keskkonnast, kus "
"nad ette tulevad. Praegu on olemas järgmised neutraalsed boonused:"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:230
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Neutral Pandora"
msgstr "Pandora neutraalne boonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pandora &ndash; this contains either a bonus or a handicap."
msgstr "Pandora sisaldab kas boonust või takistust."

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bonus Neutral Resurrect"
msgstr "Taaselustamise neutraalne boonus"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resurrect &ndash; this will resurrect any dead player."
msgstr "Taaselustamine võimaldab ellu äratada iga surnud mängija."

